regions.title: Main vehicle damage area on the race car
regions.description: This region covers the visibly damaged area of the car loaded on the tow truck, including crumpled bodywork, exposed wheel arch, and missing or bent panels.

summary: A single, continuous region of vehicle damage was detected, focused on the rear-left and side of the race car loaded on the tow truck. No cells required removal as all highlighted cells correspond to the damaged area.
